        <p>ISBN: 0385512058 READ: 2009-07-26 RATING: 7/10</p>
        <p>A good book that's mostly about networking, but also some general business smarts. Definitely read if you need more work being social.</p>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <figure class="abook" data-rating="7" data-title="Reality Check - by Guy Kawasaki" data-date="2009-03-08">
