        <p>ISBN: 0470398515 READ: 2009-04-23 RATING: 4/10</p>
        <p>Legendary investor, now 80, looks back with long-view wisdom on investing, living, and giving.</p>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <figure class="abook" data-rating="4" data-title="Management of the Absurd - by Richard Farson" data-date="2009-04-14">
      <a href="/book/ManagementOfTheAbsurd"><img src="/images/ManagementOfTheAbsurd.gif" alt="Management of the Absurd - by Richard Farson" /></a>
