        <p>ISBN: 0684830442 READ: 2009-04-14 RATING: 4/10</p>
        <p>Counter-intuitive lessons about management. Highly recommended for managers and leaders, but also teachers and parents.</p>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <figure class="abook" data-rating="4" data-title="Fooled by Randomness - by Nassim Nicholas Taleb" data-date="2008-04-05">
      <a href="/book/FooledByRandomness"><img src="/images/FooledByRandomness.gif" alt="Fooled by Randomness - by Nassim Nicholas Taleb" /></a>
