        <p>ISBN: 0307277259 READ: 2010-12-12 RATING: 3/10</p>
        <p>Thoughtful rambling observations on different lines of work. Personal tales of his time spent observing different industries like fishing, counseling, shipyards, or walking along electric towers.  Some tangential insights along the way.</p>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <figure class="abook" data-rating="3" data-title="Born Standing Up - by Steve Martin" data-date="2010-01-09">
      <a href="/book/BornStandingUp"><img src="/images/BornStandingUp.gif" alt="Born Standing Up - by Steve Martin" /></a>
