        <p>ISBN: 0787987328 READ: 2010-12-24 RATING: 2/10</p>
        <p>Personal tales, almost an autobiography, of someone who created a wide range of businesses, both successful and not.  Some insights along the way, but not many surprising ones.  I'd recommend “How to Get Rich” by Felix Dennis instead, also reviewed on this website.</p>
